y matrix elements, when full Monte Carlo RBS calculations are\nused in CORTEO code, the results from CORTEO code are in good agreement with\nthe experimental results at the low energy part of energy spectra, at this\nmoment quantitative tritium and helium analysis in thin film sample by using\nenhanced proton backscattering can be performed reliably.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Oct 2013 11:10:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
